ize: 12px; float: none;\\" align=\\"justify\\">\\u00a0<\\/div>\\r\\n<p class=\\"MsoNormal\\" style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 36pt;\\" align=\\"justify\\"><span style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<div style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12px; float: none;\\" align=\\"justify\\">\\u00a0<\\/div>\\r\\n<p class=\\"MsoNormal\\" style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 36pt;\\" align=\\"justify\\"><span style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\\">C\\u0103n c\\u1ee9 v\\u00e0o nhu c\\u1ea7u dinh d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng \\u0111\\u00e3 ghi trong b\\u1ea3ng, ti\\u1ebfn h\\u00e0nh x\\u00e2y d\\u1ef1ng kh\\u1ea9u ph\\u1ea7n \\u0103n cho v\\u1ecbt. Th\\u1ee9c \\u0103n d\\u00f9ng trong kh\\u1ea9u ph\\u1ea7n \\u0103n c\\u1ee7a vitk ph\\u1ea3i \\u0111\\u1ea1t v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1ea3m n\\u1ea3o ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng t\\u1ed1t, kh\\u00f4ng d\\u00f9ng th\\u1ee9c \\u0103n m\\u1ed1c. Th\\u1ee9c \\u0103n sau khi h\\u1ed7n h\\u1ee3p ch\\u1ec9 d\\u00f9ng 2-3 tu\\u1ea7n, kh\\u00f4ng d\\u1ef1 tr\\u1eef l\\u00e2u d\\u01b0\\u1edbi d\\u1ea1ng th\\u1ee9c \\u0103n h\\u1ed7n h\\u1ee3p. V\\u1edbi th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ea7n dinh d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng c\\u1ee7a hai lo\\u1ea1i kh\\u1ea9u ph\\u1ea7n \\u0103n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ph\\u1ed1i h\\u1ee3p (cho v\\u1ecbt con, v\\u1ecbt d\\u00f2). L\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng th\\u1ee9c \\u0103n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng h\\u00e0ng ng\\u00e0y bi\\u1ebfn \\u0111\\u1ed5i theo tu\\u1ed5i c\\u1ee7a v\\u1ecbt.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<div style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12px; float: none;\\" align=\\"justify\\">\\u00a0<\\/div>\\r\\n<p class=\\"MsoNormal\\" style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 36pt;\\" align=\\"justify\\"><span style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<div style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12px; float: none;\\" align=\\"justify\\">\\u00a0<\\/div>\\r\\n<p class=\\"MsoNormal\\" style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 36pt;\\" align=\\"justify\\"><span style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\\">V\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u1eb7c \\u0111i\\u1ec3m l\\u1edbn nhanh, c\\u00e1c gi\\u1ed1ng v\\u1ecbt h\\u01b0\\u1edbng th\\u1ecbt c\\u00f3 nhu c\\u1ea7u r\\u1ea5t kh\\u1eaft khe v\\u1ec1 th\\u1ee9c \\u0103n b\\u1ed5 sung, \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t l\\u00e0 c\\u00e1c kho\\u00e1ng vi l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng, n\\u1ebfu thi\\u1ebfu, v\\u1ecbt r\\u1ea5t d\\u1ec5 b\\u1ecb b\\u1ec7nh thi\\u1ebfu kho\\u00e1ng.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<div style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12px; float: none;\\" align=\\"justify\\">\\u00a0<\\/div>\\r\\n<p class=\\"MsoNormal\\" style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 36pt;\\" align=\\"justify\\"><span style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<div style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12px; float: none;\\" align=\\"justify\\">\\u00a0<\\/div>\\r\\n<p class=\\"MsoNormal\\" style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 36pt;\\" align=\\"justify\\"><span style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\\">V\\u1ecbt \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c nu\\u00f4i nh\\u1ed1t trong chu\\u1ed3ng, cho \\u0103n t\\u1ef1 do, t\\u1ed1t nh\\u1ea5t l\\u00e0 d\\u00f9ng m\\u00e1ng \\u0103n t\\u1ef1 \\u0111\\u1ed9ng, th\\u1ee9c \\u0103n \\u0111\\u1ed5 cho v\\u1ecbt m\\u1ed7i ng\\u00e0y m\\u1ed7i l\\u1ea7n, h\\u00e0ng ng\\u00e0y ki\\u1ec3m tra l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng th\\u1ee9c \\u0103n d\\u01b0 th\\u1eeba, thi\\u1ebfu \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ch\\u1ec9nh cho h\\u1ee3p l\\u00fd. \\u0110\\u1ec3 l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng th\\u1ee9c \\u0103n th\\u1eeba nhi\\u1ec1u trong m\\u0